Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iron-Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iron-Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iron-Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iron-Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Iron-Maidens-Bruce-Dickinson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Iron-Maiden">铁娘子乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-dickinson">布鲁斯·迪金森</a>开玩笑说，乐队将在即将到来的巡演中“做我们以前从未做过的事情”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/iron-maiden-senjutsu-review-3035836"><b>《铁娘子》——“Senjutsu”评论：富有想象力的即时经典</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队在新年前夜（12 月 31 日）分享了一段 YouTube 视频，视频中迪金森告别了 2024 年，并向歌迷介绍了他们对 2025 年的最新展望，尤其是他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-maiden-announce-2025-run-for-your-lives-european-and-uk-tour-dates-3795068">即将拉开帷幕的“Run For Your Lives”巡演在五月</a>。</p><p> “大家好。这是我 2024 年的巡演通行证。这可以让我在 2024 年去任何地方，但我现在不再需要它了，因为 2025 年将会是一些特别的事情，”歌手开始说道。 “不仅仅是因为旅游通行证。老实说，我们正在把船推出去。我不需要告诉任何人，因为基本上巡演已经卖完了。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="铁娘子 - 2025 年见！ (2024年12月31日)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WI2gwVu4bHg?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“所以对于那些买了票的人来说，就像你们所有人一样，这将是非常非常酷的。我真的很期待。我们将做一些我们以前从未做过的事情，这将成为一个永恒的清单。那么，我们在那里见。它不会在 2025 年停止。它会持续到 2026 年，因为世界上有些地方我们需要到达，但 2025 年无法到达。所以就这样吧。”</p><p>英国金属偶像即将举行的巡演将纪念他们作为乐队成立 50 周年，并将推出一个特别的歌单，其中仅包含他们前九张录音室专辑中的歌曲，从他们的同名首张专辑到《Fear Of The Dark》。此次巡演也将持续到 2026 年，不过具体日期尚未公布。请访问<a href="https://www.ironmaiden.com/tour/run-for-your-lives-world-tour/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAZHrxPib6C/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.66